    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The arrangment of various visual components for a page or pages, including drawings, graphs, photographs, or other illustrations used as supplementary to news, stories, or other text in a newspaper, magazine, brochure, online page, or other publication. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
